---
title: Cheesy Capsicum Hasselback Halloumi with Potato Wedges & Cucumber Salad
description: Get ready for a bite of cheesy perfection! Juicy, golden halloumi topped with smokey capsicum relish and ooey gooey melted cheese. Nestled alongside crisp potato wedges and a crunchy cucumber salad, this one-pan wonder is packed with bold flavours and minimal fuss.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67d7420b6526e41d967ae49d-507b50af-eef9a15e.jpeg
